{"titles": {"CN": "银色档案", "EN": "Silver Archives ", "JP": "再現記録", "KR": "은색 파일", "TW": "銀色檔案 "}, "regions": {"CN": {"ARCAFSARA001": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——萨拉托加——权限认证级别——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证完毕————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">数据解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放纪录————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————5月27日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "毫无疑问，规模庞大的重樱舰队每时每刻都在逼近。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "而我们的前线舰队数量捉襟见肘。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不但要进行作战准备，还要保证AF至圣地亚哥司令部的补给线通畅。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "阿申留防线方向也不得不防……重樱既然不知道计划已经泄露，必然会按照原定方案向那里发起进攻。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "如果MK7能够完工的话，她就能亲自带领增援舰队行动，这场战役的胜算也会更大一些。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不过做不到的事也不能强求……她现在应该比任何人都想冲上前线而不是待在后方司令部吧。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……局面压制性的不利，作为白鹰航母的大前辈……不论如何我也要打起精神来才行！", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "数据解析完毕————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放结束————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA002": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——萨拉托加——权限认证级别——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证完毕————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">数据解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放纪录————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————6月4日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "塞壬的行动十分反常，舰队今日居然在PH港西北方的安全海域内遭到攻击。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "这几日PH港西南方的安全海域内也有零星的袭击报告传来……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "虽然都只是小股敌人，但应当引起足够重视。塞壬可能正在为一次大规模袭击做准备。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "现在的前线舰队光是应对重樱的进攻就已竭尽全力，如果塞壬再发动袭击的话……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "嗯……这次我可是尽力把所有能开出海的舰队都带上了，就算塞壬真发动袭击倒也能抵挡一阵子。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "问题在于时间。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "抵达前线的时间因为沿途的塞壬阻碍而不断延迟，实际到达时间可能会是明日下午或者深夜……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "一定要赶上啊……！", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "数据解析完毕————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放结束————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA003": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——萨拉托加——权限认证级别——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证完毕————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">数据解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放纪录————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————6月5日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "大约十分钟前，收到了约克城受损情况的照片……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "除了爆炸痕迹外，还有一些宛如结晶一般的细小颗粒附在舰装的碎裂口和约克城的身体上……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "无法确定这些异常景象出现的原因是因为浓烟颗粒的附着还是拍照时的污渍。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "也许二者都有，也许二者皆无……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "战斗已成定局，我们胜利了。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "塞壬果然开始了大规模进攻，继续拖下去将会面对无法预估的风险。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "因此前线舰队正在离开前线……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……剩下的事，就交给我吧。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "数据解析完毕————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放结束————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA004": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——萨拉托加——权限认证级别——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">权限验证完毕————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">数据解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放纪录————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "……为了在对抗塞壬进攻的同时尽快抵达前线，我一面分散舰队，一面向前突击。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "终于在凌晨时分，我抵达了指定区域。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "虽然沿途分散的舰队成员尚无人抵达，我依然决定独自发起攻击。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "舰载机在夜幕中穿行着，掠过宛如星空一般的海面。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "只不过在这片黑色的星空中，闪耀着的并非群星的倒影，而是无数塞壬军舰散发出的暗淡光点。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "如果不能尽快结束战斗，所有尚未撤退的同伴都会被这股黑色的浪潮所吞噬吧。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "心中萦绕着这个念头，我加快了搜索步调。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "终于，我在一片由量产型残骸构成的明亮火场中找到了陷入大破状态的赤城、加贺和苍龙。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "飞龙似乎依靠自身动力前进了一段距离，最终还是倒在了她们稍远处的地方。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "就在我想发动攻击彻底结束战斗时，我发现了一件事————", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "在烈焰与浓烟之中还有一个人影，一个拥有巨大的舰装的塞壬人型单位。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "因为距离过远，我无法分辨具体型号。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "难道塞壬打算替我们完成最后的收尾工作么，一瞬间我产生了这样的想法。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不过这个塞壬人型单位并没有发动攻击，只是在这样极近的距离静静“欣赏”着燃烧的重樱舰队。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "我也将舰载机隐藏在云层之中，静静观察着事态的变化。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "然后……冲击出现了。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "以赤城为中心，向四周发出了一股，我隔着仪器不知道应该怎么形容的……肉眼可见的红黑色冲击波？", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "红黑色的冲击将塞壬人型单位击出数十米远。当然，这也可能是它主动采取规避手段的表现。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "冲击波的影响的范围极广，我的舰载机虽然因为距离过远幸免于难，但是更近一些的塞壬量产型舰队就没这么好运了。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "奇怪的是，处于冲击正中心位置的赤城与加贺却好像没有受到任何影响。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "几乎与此同时，一个红黑色身影凭空出现在赤城与塞壬人型指挥者之间。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "因为相同的原因，我无法看清那个身影的面目。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不过…………我认为，她应该是舰船。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "而且我对她有一种仿佛曾经在哪里见过的熟悉感。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "究竟是为什么呢………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "萨拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "数据解析异常————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放中断————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "领航员-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "EN": {"Archive Log I": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Access authentication in progress–––<br>", "Archived data from [CV-3 Saratoga] –– Access Level: II<br>", "Access authentication successful–––<br>", "Accessing data–––<br>", "Starting data playback–––<br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "Um, today is May 27th.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "The location the Sakura Empire fleet was discovered at... should be here...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Oh, right! That's where it was!", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hmm... Even though I was the one who wrote the report, I had to destroy the original after giving it to the Naval HQ...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "That sure throws a wrench in things, doesn't it?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But, thank your lucky stars that Sister Sara is so resourceful... I doubt any other girl would be able to salvage the documents.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Now, if you want to know about the \"Black Dragon,\" I'm sure you'll find that out on your own sooner or later.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "By the way, don't put Sister Sara's minor grumbling on the records, pretty please?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Understood. Deleting records of recording log.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Deletion complete. Continuing playback of recording log.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Archive Log II": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Access authentication in progress–––<br>", "Archived data from [CV-3 Saratoga] –– Access Level: II<br>", "Access authentication successful–––<br>", "Accessing data–––<br>", "Starting data playback–––<br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "–––Action Report Records:", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Sirens are appearing one after another in the waters near a remote island base in the NW Sector.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Furthermore, the Sirens conducted a number of attacks of secured sectors.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"While each attack consisted only of a few ships, we believe that this is a precursor to a large-scale Siren offensive.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Yeah, yeah. I know, I'm taking this seriously, okay?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "The reason we moved our reserves up here was in anticipation of this offensive.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I had no idea we were in the middle of a Reenactment back then, and Commander wasn't around either.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Huh? We were all panicking at the time?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "C'mon, TB, just play back the next thing already.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Understood. Ending playback of recording log.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Beginning search and analysis for the next recording log.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Archive Log III": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Access authentication in progress–––<br>", "Archived data from [CV-3 Saratoga] –– Access Level: II<br>", "Access authentication successful–––<br>", "Accessing data–––<br>", "Starting data playback–––<br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "\"–––Action Report Records\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Aircraft carrier Yorktown was heavily injured during the Siren offensive, but thanks to everyone's efforts, the Sirens were pushed back successfully.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Damage Report Status ––– CV-5 Yorktown ––– Heavy Damage\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Though her condition is stable, her rigging was heavily damaged, necessitating her to be transferred from the front lines for long-term medical care.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"–––In addition, the phenomenon of 'Microlayer' particulate matter adhesion to her rigging was confirmed.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Anyway, what's important is that we all made it back in one piece.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "At least we retrieved Yorktown safely, though I have no idea what this \"Microlayer\" thing is...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "After all, I was so focused on trying to stop the Sirens that I couldn't worry about other things.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "TB, sweetie, can you give me the details on what's going on with the Sakura Empire?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Understood. Ending playback of recording log.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Beginning search and analysis for the next recording log.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Silver Archives IV": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Access authentication in progress–––<br>", "Archived data from [CV-3 Saratoga] –– Access Level: II<br>", "Access authentication successful–––<br>", "Accessing data–––<br>", "Starting data playback–––<br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "\"The fleet responsible for chasing down the Siren stragglers detected signals from a Sakura Empire ship to the west.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"The aforementioned ship rushed to the source of the signal to investigate.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "That aforementioned ship is yours truly, Sister Sara!", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Carrier-based reconnaissance revealed a large amount of Siren wreckage in the western sector.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"This suggested that a battle had broken out between the Sirens and another large fleet.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Because the Eagle Union had only deployed ships to the eastern sectors, we can conclude that the combatants were–––\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"The Sakura Fleet.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I remember seeing Akagi, Kaga, Souryuu, and... yeah, even Hiryuu. Everyone looked like they had been through hell.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Even if I wanted to help, I was simply too far away... Besides, given how tricky things are with the Crimson Axis...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"In addition to the Sakura Empire fleet, another Siren command unit was observed nearby.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"The humanoid command unit was not observed attacking the Sakura Empire fleet.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Finally, considering the damage inflicted upon the Sakura Empire fleet, we can conclude that the command unit did not need to participate in combat to achieve its desired results.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "That's why I tried to send a fleet after it as quickly as possible!", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I even had my planes fly up higher to get a better grasp of the whole situation.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But in the end, I couldn't figure out what the Siren was up to...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Regarding the special phenomenon...\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"A shockwave with an observable reddish-black 'color' appeared around CV Akagi.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"In addition to repelling the humanoid Siren, almost all mass-produced ships in range of the shockwave were destroyed.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"However, the other ships of the Sakura Empire were not visibly affected by the effects of this shockwave.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "\"Based upon the extent of the damage inflicted to these carriers, this attack was unlikely to have been carried out using any weapons we currently know of.\"", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I seem to remember... seeing someone else there for a brief moment as well...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But who was it...?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I could've sworn I've seen her at some point...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But when...?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Who was it...?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "Saratoga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Playback error, missing file path.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ending playback.", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "JP": {"「再現」の記録・Ⅰ": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限確認中―――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">CV-3空母「サラトガ」記録データ・アクセス権限「Ⅱ」</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限を確認しました――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">データ解析中――</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">ログ再生開始</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "ええと、今日は5月27日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「重桜」艦隊の発見記録…たしかここにあるはず…", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あったあった、ここにあるのね", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "ふぅ…サラトガちゃんが自分でレポートを書いたのに、上層部に渡したら原本も削除しなきゃならないなんて", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "こういうのは本当に不便なんだよね＞＜", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "調べさせられたのがサラトガちゃんでよかったわね…もしほかの子だったらこの資料にたどり着くのさえ一苦労しそう", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "まあ、「ぶらっくどらごん」ちゃんのことだし、多分自分で探してもすぐ出てくるんじゃない？", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "と、ここまではサラトガちゃんの愚痴、記録するのはNGでお願いよ", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "了解しました。記録ログの書き込みは削除します", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "削除が完了しました。引き続きログの再生を開始します――", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "「再現」の記録・Ⅱ": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限確認中―――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">CV-3空母「サラトガ」記録データ・アクセス権限「Ⅱ」</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限を確認しました――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">データ解析中――</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">ログ再生開始</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "――「作戦記録」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「大洋にあるユニオン離島基地の北西部にセイレーンの出現が相次ぎ――」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「さらに、安全海域だったエリアにも、セイレーンによる船団襲撃が発生した」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「いずれも数隻程度の規模だったが、上層部はセイレーンによる大規模攻勢の前兆であると推測」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "そうそう。そういうところはちゃんと慎重にやったほうがいいわね", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "こちらに艦隊戦力を振り分けたのもこの攻勢に備えるためだったわね…", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あのときは「再現」のことだと知らなかったし、指揮官も現場にいなかったから", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "確かみんなバタバタしてたっけ？", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "TBちゃん、次の記録をお願いね", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "了解しました。記録ログの再生を終了します", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "次の記録ログの検索・解析を開始します", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "「再現」の記録・Ⅲ": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限確認中―――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">CV-3空母「サラトガ」記録データ・アクセス権限「Ⅱ」</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限を確認しました――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">データ解析中――</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">ログ再生開始</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "――「作戦記録」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「空母ヨークタウンがセイレーンの攻撃で重傷を受けたが、各艦の尽力でセイレーンの撃退に成功」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「損傷状況　ヨークタウン　大破」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「命に別状はないものの、艤装の損傷が大きく、後方移送と長期療養が必要と判断され――」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「――また、艤装の破損面における『粒子状の物質』の付着……という現象も確認された」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "とにかく、あの戦いには無事に勝ったわね", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "ヨークタウンは無事回復したし、あの謎の粒子状の物質が何だったのかも分からずじまい", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "まあ、あのときはセイレーンの攻勢阻止に全力をかけていたから心配することもあまりなかったわ", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "TBちゃん、次は重桜の動向の記録ね", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "了解しました。記録ログの再生を終了します", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "次の記録ログの検索・解析を開始します", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "「再現」の記録・Ⅳ": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限確認中―――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">CV-3空母「サラトガ」記録データ・アクセス権限「Ⅱ」</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">アクセス権限を確認しました――</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">データ解析中――</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">ログ再生開始</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "「セイレーン残党の掃討を行った艦隊は、エリアの西側に重桜艦船の信号をキャッチした」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「先行した艦船は信号の発信源へと急行し、状況の確認を行った」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "つまりこのサラトガちゃんのことね！", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「艦載機による偵察では、エリアの西側にセイレーンの残骸が多数確認されており――」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「また、セイレーンと大規模艦隊の間で戦闘が発生した痕跡が観測されている」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「同エリアにおいてはユニオン艦隊は東側にのみ展開していたことから、セイレーンと交戦したのは――」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「重桜艦隊であることが確実だと判断した」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "赤城に加賀、そして蒼龍……ううん、飛龍もいたわね。しかもみんな結構ダメージを食らっていたわ", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "支援したくても距離が遠すぎるし、なによりレッドアクシズとの件もあった…", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「重桜の空母艦隊のほか、同エリアではセイレーンの指揮ユニットの存在が観測された」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「指揮ユニット――人型セイレーンは重桜艦隊に攻撃する行動が見受けられなかった」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「最も、重桜艦隊の損傷からすると、指揮ユニットが攻撃するまでもなく、量産艦や『駒』だけで勝敗を決することが可能だったと思われる」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "だからサラトガちゃんが後続の艦隊に急行するよう指示して", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "さらに、偵察機の高度を上げて状況を注視し続けたわ", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あのセイレーン、結局何をしていたんだろう…", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「特殊現象の記録について」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「空母・赤城を中心に、赤黒い『色』をした衝撃波が発生」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「人型セイレーンを撃退したほか、衝撃波が届いた範囲内の量産艦をほぼ全部撃破した」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「一方、加賀や蒼龍・飛龍はその衝撃波を受けても特に影響を受けたような様子は観測できなかった」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "「空母たちの損傷度合いから察すると、既知の兵装からこのような攻撃を繰り出す可能性は低いと判断できる」", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "（あの衝撃波が発生したとき、たしかほかの「誰か」が急に現れたわね…）", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "（顔とか全然はっきりと見えなかったけど）", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "（海の上にいつの間にか現れてたけど、多分艦船なのかな）", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "一体誰だったのかな……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "サラトガ", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "記録ログ、エラー箇所を検知しました", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "再生、終了しました", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "KR": {"ARCAFSARA001": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 중————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——새러토가——권한 인증 레벨——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 완료————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">데이터 분석 중————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">기록 재생 중————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————5월 27일", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "큰 규모의 사쿠라 엠파이어 함대가 지금도 이쪽으로 다가오고 있다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "하지만 우리의 전선 함대는 턱없이 부족하다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "작전 준비뿐 아니라 AF부터 샌디에이고 사령부까지 보급선도 원활하게 확보해야 한다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "알류산 방어선도 경계해야 한다... 사쿠라 엠파이어는 계획 누설에 대해서 모르기 때문에 정해진 계획대로 공격해올 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "MK7이 예정대로 완공된다면 직접 증원 함대를 끌고 움직일 수 있겠지? 그렇다면 이번 전투의 승률도 크게 올라갈 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "하지만 할 수 없는 일을 강요할 수는 없다... 후방 사령부에서 대기하기보다는 누구보다도 전선에 뛰어들고 싶어 할 테니까.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "...불리한 상황이지만 이글 유니온 항공모함의 대선배로서... 정신을 차려야 해!", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "데이터 분석 완료————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "재생 종료————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA002": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 중————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——새러토가——권한 인증 레벨——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 완료————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">데이터 분석 중————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">기록 재생 중————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————6월 4일", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "세이렌의 행동이 이상하다. 함대가 PH항의 북서쪽 안전 해역에서 적의 공격을 받기도 했다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "요 며칠 PH항 남서쪽의 안전 해역에서도 습격 소식이 전해져 왔다...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "소규모 습격이긴 하지만 눈여겨봐야 한다. 어쩌면 세이렌이 대규모 습격을 준비하고 있는 것일 수도 있다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "전선 함대는 사쿠라 엠파이어의 공격을 받아내는 것만으로도 벅찬데, 여기에 세이렌이 다시 습격을 한다면...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "음... 이번에는 동원할 수 있는 모든 함대를 데리고 왔으니 세이렌이 정말 습격한다고 해도 한동안은 막아낼 수 있을 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "문제는 시간이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "전선에 도착하는 시간이 세이렌의 방해로 점점 지연되고 있다. 실제로 도착하는 것은 내일 오후나 늦은 밤이 될 수도 있겠는데...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "얼른 따라잡아야 해...!", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "데이터 분석 완료————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "재생 종료————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA003": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 중————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——새러토가——권한 인증 레벨——IV——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 완료————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">데이터 분석 중————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">기록 재생 중————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————6월 5일", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "10분 전, 요크타운의 피해 상황을 담은 사진을 받았다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "폭발의 흔적뿐 아니라 알갱이와 같은 결정이 장비의 틈과 요크타운의 몸에 잔뜩 붙어 있었지...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "이런 이상한 현상이 주변에 있던 알갱이가 붙은 것인지, 아니면 사진을 찍을 때 있던 얼룩인지 알 수는 없다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "어쩌면 둘 다일 수도, 둘 다 아닐 수도...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "전세는 굳혀졌다. 우리의 승리야.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "세이렌이 대규모 공세를 퍼부었기 때문에 계속 미루다 가는 예측할 수 없는 위험에 처하게 될 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "그래서 전선 함대가 자리를 비운 상태니까...", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "...남은 일은 나에게 맡겨줘.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "데이터 분석 완료————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "재생 종료————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA004": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 중————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——새러토가——권한 인증 레벨——V——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">권한 인증 완료————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">데이터 분석 중————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">기록 재생 중————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "...세이렌의 공격에 대항하며 빠르게 전선에 도착하기 위해 함대를 분산시켜 돌격했다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "새벽 즈음, 드디어 지정한 구역에 도착할 수 있었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "흩어진 함대원 중에 도착한 사람이 없었기 때문에 혼자서 공격을 하기로 결심했다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "함재기들이 별빛처럼 어둠 속을 헤치며 바다를 스쳤다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "다만 이 검은 별하늘 속에, 반짝이는 것은 별들의 그림자가 아닌 수많은 세이렌 함선이 내는 어두운 빛이었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "이 전투를 빨리 끝내지 못한다면 아직 철수하지 못한 동료들은 이 검은 물결 속에 삼켜질 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "이런 생각이 머릿속에 계속 맴돌고 있기 때문에 수색에 박차를 가했다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "드디어 불타는 양산형의 잔해 속에서 크게 파괴된 아카기, 카가와 소류를 발견했다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "히류는 자신의 동력으로 어느 정도 전진했는지 그녀들과 조금 떨어진 곳에 있었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "공격을 진행해 전투를 끝내려고 했을 때쯤, 한 가지 사실을 발견했다————", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "화염과 연기 사이로 거대한 장비를 갖춘 인간형 세이렌이 있었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "거리가 너무 멀어서 구체적인 모델은 확인할 수 없었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "설마 세이렌이 마무리를 대신해 줄 생각인가? 순간 그런 생각이 들었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "하지만 인간형 세이렌은 공격을 하지 않고 그 자리에서 조용히 불타고 있는 사쿠라 엠파이어 함대를 '감상'하고 있었다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "나 역시 함재기를 구름 속에 숨긴 채 사태를 지켜보았다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "그리고... 큰 충격이 일어났다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "아카기를 중심으로 사방에 발사되는... 이것을 뭐라고 표현해야 할까? 육안으로 확인할 수 있는 검붉은 충격파?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "검붉은 충격파는 인간형 세이렌을 수십 미터나 날려 보냈다. 물론, 그것이 직접 피했다고 할 수도 있을 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "충격파의 범위는 매우 넓었다. 내 함재기는 거리가 멀어 다행히 휘말리지 않았지만, 세이렌 양산형 함대에게 그런 행운은 일어나지 않았다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "이상한 것은 충격의 중심에 있던 아카기와 카가는 아무런 영향을 받지 않은 듯하다는 것이다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "그와 거의 동시에 검붉은 그림자가 아카기와 인간형 세이렌 지휘자 사이에 나타났다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "역시나 같은 이유로 그 모습을 자세히 확인하지는 못했다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "하지만... 아마도 함선이라고 생각한다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "게다가 어디선가 본 것 같은 익숙한 느낌이 든다.", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "대체 왜일까...?", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "새러토가", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "데이터 분석 오류————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "재생 중지————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "네비게이터-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "TW": {"ARCAFSARA001": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——薩拉托加——權限認證級別——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證完畢————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">數據解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放紀錄————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————5月27日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "毫無疑問，規模龐大的重櫻艦隊每時每刻都在逼近。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "而我們的前線艦隊數量捉襟見肘。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不但要進行作戰準備，還要保證AF至聖地牙哥司令部的補給線通暢。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "阿留申防線方向也不得不防……重櫻既然不知道計劃已經洩露，必然會按照原定方案向那裡發起進攻。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "如果MK7能夠完工的話，她就能親自帶領增援艦隊行動，這場戰役的勝算也會更大一些。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不過做不到的事也不能強求……她現在應該比任何人都想衝上前線而不是待在後方司令部吧。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……局面壓制性的不利，作為白鷹航母的大前輩……不論如何我也要打起精神來才行！", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "數據解析完畢————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放結束————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA002": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——薩拉托加——權限認證級別——II——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證完畢————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">數據解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放紀錄————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————6月4日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "塞壬的行動十分反常，艦隊今日居然在PH港西北方的安全海域內遭到攻擊。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "這幾日PH港西南方的安全海域內也有零星的襲擊報告傳來……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "雖然都只是小股敵人，但應當引起足夠重視。塞壬可能正在為一次大規模襲擊做準備。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "現在的前線艦隊光是應對重櫻的進攻就已竭盡全力，如果塞壬再發動襲擊的話……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "嗯……這次我可是盡力把所有能開出海的艦隊都帶上了，就算塞壬真發動襲擊倒也能抵擋一陣子。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "問題在於時間。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "抵達前線的時間因為沿途的塞壬阻礙而不斷延遲，實際到達時間可能會是明日下午或者深夜……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "一定要趕上啊……！", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "數據解析完畢————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放結束————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA003": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——薩拉托加——權限認證級別——IV——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證完畢————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">數據解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放紀錄————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "————6月5日", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "大約十分鐘前，收到了約克鎮受損情況的照片……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "除了爆炸痕跡外，還有一些宛如結晶一般的細小顆粒附在艦裝的碎裂口和約克鎮的身體上……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "無法確定這些異常景象出現的原因是因為濃煙顆粒的附著還是拍照時的污漬。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "也許二者都有，也許二者皆無……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "戰鬥已成定局，我們勝利了。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "塞壬果然開始了大規模進攻，繼續拖下去將會面對無法預估的風險。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "因此前線艦隊正在離開前線……", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……剩下的事，就交給我吧。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "數據解析完畢————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放結束————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "ARCAFSARA004": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證中————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">——CV-3——薩拉托加——權限認證級別——V——</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">權限驗證完畢————————————</span><br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">數據解析中————————————</span> <br>", "<span style=\"font-size: 0.850em;\">正在播放紀錄————————————</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "bsm-2", "bgName": "star_level_bg_1100", "say": "……為了在對抗塞壬進攻的同時盡快抵達前線，我一面分散艦隊，一面向前突擊。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "終於在凌晨時分，我抵達了指定區域。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "雖然沿途分散的艦隊成員尚無人抵達，我依然決定獨自發起攻擊。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "艦載機在夜幕中穿行著，掠過宛如星空一般的海面。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "只不過在這片黑色的星空中，閃耀著的並非群星的倒影，而是無數塞壬軍艦散發出的暗淡光點。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "如果不能盡快結束戰鬥，所有尚未撤退的同伴都會被這股黑色的浪潮所吞噬吧。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "心中縈繞著這個念頭，我加快了搜索步調。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "終於，我在一片由量產型殘骸構成的明亮火場中找到了陷入大破狀態的赤城、加賀和蒼龍。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "飛龍似乎依靠自身動力前進了一段距離，最終還是倒在了她們稍遠處的地方。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "就在我想發動攻擊徹底結束戰鬥時，我發現了一件事————", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "在烈焰與濃煙之中還有一個人影，一個擁有巨大的艦裝的塞壬人型單位。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "因為距離過遠，我無法分辨具體型號。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "難道塞壬打算替我們完成最後的收尾工作嗎，一瞬間我產生了這樣的想法。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不過這個塞壬人型單位並沒有發動攻擊，只是在這樣極近的距離靜靜“欣賞”著燃燒的重櫻艦隊。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "我也將艦載機隱藏在雲層之中，靜靜觀察著事態的變化。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "然後……衝擊出現了。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "以赤城為中心，向四周發出了一股，我隔著儀器不知道應該怎麼形容的……肉眼可見的紅黑色衝擊波？", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "紅黑色的衝擊將塞壬人型單位擊出數十米遠。當然，這也可能是它主動採取迴避手段的表現。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "衝擊波影響的範圍極廣，我的艦載機雖然因為距離過遠倖免於難，但是更近一些的塞壬量產型艦隊就沒這麼好運了。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "奇怪的是，處於衝擊正中心位置的赤城與加賀卻好像沒有受到任何影響。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "幾乎與此同時，一個紅黑色身影憑空出現在赤城與塞壬人型指揮者之間。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "因為相同的原因，我無法看清那個身影的面目。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不過…………我認為，她應該是艦船。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "而且我對她有一種彷彿曾經在哪裡見過的熟悉感。", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "究竟是為什麼呢………………", "actor": 107030, "actorName": "薩拉托加", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "數據解析異常————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "播放中斷————————————", "actor": 900284, "actorName": "領航員-TB", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}}}